Tɔnɛ  kɛna awayɩ tɛtɛ kpɩnɛ huyuŋ nɛ mbʊ pakɩlʊna-yɛ labɩnaʊ yɔ mbʊlɛ naakomna, huyiŋ, hulasi, tokonaa, waacinaa, kɔɔkasɩ, sɩsɩ huyiŋ, kpacanaa tola, tɔŋ nimasi mbʊ payaɣ se hikasi yɔ yaa ɛzɩ mba palakɩ fadɩŋ yɔ pɛ-tɛ alɩfaatʊ wendu yaa pɛñɛyɩ tɔna ana nɛ pacanɩna nabʊyʊ. Calaɣ taa lɛ, tɛtɛkpɩna wena a-tɔna pakɩlʊ labɩnaʊ yɔ anaa lɛ wena apaɣlɩ camɩyɛ yɔ ɛzɩ tɛyɛ naŋ yaa yaa tɛyɛ namɩŋ yɔ. Pɩtasɩ ɛlɛ pɩtɛkɛ tɛyɛ namaɩŋ yeke tɔna palakɩna, palakɩna tʊma ana ɖɔɖɔ nɛ ɖɩɣa wondu ɖɔɖɔ. Paakpakʊ-yɛ yem nɛ papaɣzɩ tʊma kɛ labɩnaʊ. Pakʊ pɩtɛ kpɩna ana ɛlɛ, pelitu a-tɔnɩŋ nɛ pɔhɔɔ camɩyɛ nɛ pɩwɛɛ tɔnɩɩɩ yaa ɛzɩ powona menziininaa taa nɛ pɔhɔɔ. Tokonaa nɛ pantalɔna mba pɛñɛyʊ na tɔna ana yɔ, pʊlʊkɩna nikaɣ kamaɣfɛyɩ. Pɩwɛɛ mbʊ lɛ, tɔna wɛ ndɩ ndɩ pɩlɩɩna kpɩnɛ nɖɩ pelita ɖɩtɔnʊ, pɔhɔɔ nɛ size palabɩna yɔ a-yɔɔ.
